{"tid":755761,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【時鐘酒店趣聞】邊段時間最多人偷情？有師奶帶埋個仔去爆房（足本版）","createTime":"2018-07-25T12:40:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T05:49:59.000Z","uid":67500,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"23c1aa714ae1fe2535e086279b696f8745e36a41","tid":755761,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T12:40:29.000Z","msg":"時代變了，傳統的時鐘酒店和賓館行業，也要改變 ..。<br />\n<br />\n「我們這行不會被淘汰的，始終香港賓館仍然有得做。」在旺角區經營時鐘賓館二十多年的區太，雖然覺得他們仍然可生存，但她也承認現在少了年青男女光顧這種傳統的時鐘賓館，「現在主要做大陸人生意，多數是自由行。」<br />\n<br />\n她又說，現在主要過夜客多，「時租客有甚麼用，現在一日也沒有一個。我們做了很長時間，一向都是做自由行客。」至於每個月有多少生意額，她就說不能透露。<br />\n<br />\n時鐘賓館，每日都有繁忙時段，「以時間性來說，說是廿四小時營業，也有繁忙及非繁忙時間，真正的繁忙時間，一定是中午十二時半開始，至二時半。另一段時間，就是下午五時至凌晨一兩點。」<br />\n<br />\n這一行，也有行很多得意趣事。「例如早上，有人會帶小朋友返幼稚園、小學後，就會跟情人去鬼混。尤其是名校區的九龍塘，而尖沙咀也很多。中午時間，就是香港人所謂的偷跳時間，食飯之前及之後，人們都愛做那回事。」<br />\n<br />\n去時鐘賓館的，什麼人也有，「客人做行街的有，教書也有，看着他們放中午堂<br />\n，就跑去親密時光。」有些情況，想也想不到，「有些非常好笑，拿著蔬菜，甚至帶着兒子，叫房東幫忙看管兒子兩三小時也有，所以甚麼客人也有。」<br />\n<br />\n採訪：劉名<br />\n攝影：林金展<br />\n<br />\n立即下載《壹週刊》Apps，隨時隨地睇盡時政專題、深度偵查、娛樂熱話！<br />\n按此連結：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/next28app\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fnext28app&d=O3GdHONW6uTLcbHmVovOSL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=c43f34b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/next28app</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/spot/20180725/607822\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fspot%2F20180725%2F607822&d=O3GdHONW6uTLcbHmVovOSL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=3c5be750\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fspot%2F20180725%2F607822&h=b8a0358a\" target=\"_blank\">http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/spot/20180725/607822</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌人妻....睇到扯扯地"},{"pid":"5a155499baf423927d4bfc7189333c7703d1760a","tid":755761,"uid":6222,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T12:59:14.000Z","msg":"有無咁緊火 帶埋個仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6af824b4020fc3df368e988fce7f186d7351f32a","tid":755761,"uid":29675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T13:01:23.000Z","msg":"LUNCH Q<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de7391f034569b029eaf5ecf2342210373d93567","tid":755761,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T13:42:40.000Z","msg":"雞"},{"pid":"0b1aff9d7a6e320c61ca70dd2ae9a992d2104385","tid":755761,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T13:44:11.000Z","msg":"召喚blackberry巴打"},{"pid":"3720e1a4540da0322fa8cffc34e79e9170d746ae","tid":755761,"uid":141917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T14:23:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">想屌</span></span>"},{"pid":"e3f5c77719a55a1e442af0cc21d8f11aa9d84bbc","tid":755761,"uid":67500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T14:24:43.000Z","msg":"採訪：劉名<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f85991a90f19f0cbab2d40a7686f1308a4dda21","tid":755761,"uid":47359,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0b1aff9d7a6e320c61ca70dd2ae9a992d2104385","tid":755761,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T13:44:11.000Z","msg":"召喚blackberry巴打"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T14:50:59.000Z","msg":"五毛沙田you<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/225052_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F225052_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=1a622f0e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"49ae71c269c591f1e4c6fe99524d7553b5004c94","tid":755761,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3f5c77719a55a1e442af0cc21d8f11aa9d84bbc","tid":755761,"uid":67500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime